com.cmput301.cs.project.models

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cmput301.cs.project.models.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Saveable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements Saveable
    This class allows for the creation of and association of a username and user id to a user that will allow the user to log into the application and use it.

    each user is assigned a unique ID on construction which is important when loading claims to know when user is a claimant and when they are an approver.

    This class is used throughout most of the app because alot of items are tagged to their user. References can be found in:

    • App
      • createUser()
      • getUser()
    • ClaimListActivity
      • onCreate()
    • LoginActivity
      • login(View)
    • ClaimListController
      • ClaimListController(User, ClaimsList)
    • Claim
      • canApprover(User)
      • getClaimant()
    • ClaimsList
    • Comment
      • Comment(String, User)
      • getApprover()
